title: Episode 25 w/ Thirstin Howl The 3rd & The Drink Champs family

description:
N.O.R.E. and DJ EFN are the Drink Champs. In this episode the guys drink it up with Lo Life general Thirstin Howl the 3rd and the extended Drink Champs family. The guys talk about Thirstin's history with Eminem, the founding of the Lo Life's, and a lot more. --- Support this podcast: https://anchor.fm/drinkchamps/support
